    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8039-bc61-d29d43399a46",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Dropout is worrysome for academic institutions and preventing it should be regarded as important both for the institutions and students. Authors present a model that uses Naive Bayes to predict dropout. The predictive model is followed by a feature analysis. ",
